profile: With professional, dedicated plumbing service to all major cities and surrounding areas in Alberta, and with some of the best plumbers in the industry, The Gentlemen Plumbers work hard to exceed your expectations and deliver quality. If you need a plumber, call us today for plumbing or heating issues, leaky sinks and faucets, clogged drains, toilet, bathtub and shower repairs, furnace cleaning and repairs, hot water tanks and tankless hot water heaters, furnace installation and maintenance, trenchless pipe repair, camera sewer inspection, and more! We have local branches in Calgary, Edmonton, Red Deer, Lethbridge, and Medicine Hat, with extended service all over Southern Alberta, including Camrose, Sherwood Park, St. Albert, Airdrie, High River, Crossfield, Carstairs, Olds, Innisfail, Wetaskiwin, Leduc, Lacombe, Okotoks, Nanton, Taber, Cardston, Didsbury, Brooks, Crowsnest Pass, Cochrane, Strathmore, Sundre, Three Hills, Ponoka, Fort Macleod, Pincher Creek, Bowden, Fort Saskatchewan, Chestermere, Sylvan Lake, Spruce Grove, and Stony Plain.

Furnace Fellas is your trusted brand when you need any Furnace or Plumbing repairs.  We are always looking for ways to help improve our brand experience. We live by our core values. "honesty, passion, teamwork, purpose"  we as a team look forward to servicing your home or business and making sure that we give the best possible service, industry leading warranties and fully trained staff from the first phone call to the final walk through.

Furnace Fellas is a leader in the service industry, we guarantee when our team services your home comfort system we will make it the best it can be with our full time service department we make sure that you are fully aware of any possible problems with our full comprehensive inspection.

Furnace Fellas wants you to know that we care. We will be able to work with you through any problems that you may have with your heating and cooling systems.

Here at Highcliffe Mechanical we are committed in providing competitive pricing with unparalleled service. We provide Residential and Commercial Plumbing, Heating, Gasfitting and Air Conditioning service to Calgary, Airdrie, Chestermere, Cochrane, Okotoks and multiple surrounding areas. 
From a leaky faucet, clogged drain, no heat or hot water, renovations, retro-fits, new installs through to new builds our dedicated team of professionals are here for you. With our 24/7 emergency service you can count on Highcliffe. Don't hesitate to call or message, we are here to help!

profile:
Established in November 2001, Monty’s Plumbing & Heating Services Inc. is trade-certified and licensed for business in Airdrie, Calgary and surrounding area. From our company’s inception, our team has strived to deliver exceptional workmanship and customer care with a combined industry experience of 30 years. Today, we continue to grow and solidify our reputation, thanks to our loyal clients—and our new customers, too!


We are proud to support our community, not only by meeting their plumbing and heating needs, but through local community organizations. This includes from time to time the Airdrie Food Bank, And various youth related programs or events.


We specialize in Fireplaces, Furnaces, Bathroom & Kitchen Renovations, BBQ's, Ventilation, Toilets, Tubs, Showers, Dryers, Faucets, Sinks, Dishwashers, Ranges, Garburators, Icemakers, Garage Heaters, Gas Fitting, UV Lights, Air Exchangers, Air Cleaners, Hot Water Heating, Water Treatment, Drains, Sewers, Humidifiers, Hot Water Tanks and more.

profile:
As a versatile, full-service Plumbing Company we are able to offer a wide range of residential and commercial services. Whether you need your water heater replaced, a drain clog removed, a boiler repaired, or a gas line installed we have you covered! 

We are committed to providing comprehensive, long-lasting solutions rather than quick fixes, and we always take the time to explain our work before we start, so you understand what’s happening and why. We also warranty our workmanship on everything we do, and will inform you of all your available options. We won’t recommend a replacement if we can carry out repairs on your existing plumbing or heating system. 

Our Journeymen Plumbers and Gasfitters are fully licensed, insured, have 20+ years of residential and commercial services, and are committed to doing a job right the first time! No matter what your plumbing issue is, we’ve probably seen and provided the plumbing solution before. We offer 24/7 Emergency Plumbing Services for plumbing fixes that just can't wait, free estimates, and are certified Cross Connection Control specialists.  
If you live in Calgary, Airdrie or surrounding areas contact us today at 403-945-8324 to schedule your next plumbing service, or visit us online at www.kaitechplumbing.ca to learn more about our services.

Well it has been a testing time for everyone this past few months..... i want to offer my plumbing services to anyone that needs some work done. I want to stress that i am healthy and will be taking all precautions when i come and do work at your place. I not only want to protect myself and my family but yours as well. I will he wearing a mask the entire job and using hand sanitizer and lysol wipes and a clean uniform every day. If you need anything done send me a message and i will get you a quote right away. 


I work in Calgary, Airdrie and surrounding areas. If you want to get a hold of me you can give me a call, text or email. I offer competitive rates and am very quick to either give an estimate or come complete your job. No job is to big or to small.
